newsitem.title: AUSTRIA: Lenzing shares suspended in Vienna-bourse.
newsitem.headline: Lenzing shares suspended in Vienna-bourse.

text.p: Shares in viscose maker Lenzing have been suspended from trade in Vienna until 0900 GMT pending an important announcement, the stock exchange said on Thursday.
Lenzing is due to present its half-year results at 0830 GMT. -- Vienna Newsroom, 43-1-53112-258
